# 🇩🇰 ShuddhiCheck AI – Phase II: Denmark Readiness

This folder contains the official readiness brief and rollout plan for ShuddhiCheck AI’s Phase II expansion into Denmark.

📄 [Download Denmark Readiness Brief (PDF)](./ShuddhiCheckAI_PhaseII_Denmark_Readiness.pdf)

---

## 📌 Key Highlights

- National AI strategy in healthcare with pilot-friendly environments
- Strong data protection compliance via Datatilsynet (Danish DPA)
- EU AI Act early adoption country
- Centralized digital infrastructure (Sundhed.dk, MedCom)
- Bilingual rollout: Danish (required), English (accepted in pilots)

---

## 🏛️ Governance & Innovation Partners

- Ministry of Health – Denmark
- Danish Data Protection Agency (Datatilsynet)
- Sundhed.dk – National Health Portal
- MedCom – Health Information Exchange Standards Body
- Key innovation hospitals: Aarhus, Rigshospitalet, Odense

---

## 🌐 Language & Localization

| Language | Status |
|----------|--------|
| **Danish** | ✅ Official language; required for public health dashboards and communication |
| **English** | ✅ Widely used (86% population fluent); ideal for pilot phases and outreach |

🟢 Dual-language dashboards (Danish + English) supported for rollout.

---

## 🛠️ Next Steps

- Upload the PDF readiness brief
- Engage with MedCom and Sundhed.dk
- Localize pilot dashboards for AI compliance and GDPR audit support
